For this assignment I created a game called Void Runner using p5.js. I made it so the player controls a small square on the screen and has to move around using the WASD or arrow keys to avoid getting hit. I added three different types of enemies that spawn from the edges of the screen and chase the player around. I also added a shooting mechanic where the player clicks the mouse to fire bullets in whatever direction they want. I gave each enemy type a different speed and a different number of hit points so they would all feel different to fight. I included a health bar at the bottom of the screen that goes down every time an enemy touches the player. The goal I set for the game is to shoot through the enemies and reach the glowing exit on the right side of the screen to win.
